title: Import of skim milk powder in Canada 2021
summary: The graph illustrates the Import of skim in Canada 2021 .
The Import generally falls from January to July .
It then climbs rapidly to the peak at over 400000 Tonnes in October .
gold: A line chart about the import of skim milk powder in Canada in the year 2021 . The import of skim milk powder was volatile throughout the year 2021 , with hug swings in July , but a large decline come the end of the year , reaching the lows of below 150 tonnes imported .
